{"tid":1149214,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"HBO 最新英雄影集《守護者 Watchmen》首波預告正式放送","createTime":"2019-05-11T04:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T03:00:52.000Z","uid":119778,"like":27,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"398b71bd97851bc5d6175a7a5a5b1478c132446c","tid":1149214,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:05:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zymgtV99Rko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzymgtV99Rko&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=666451dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zymgtV99Rko</a><br />\n<br />\n2009 年 Warner Bros. 上映《Watchmen》這部超級英雄電影，改編自 DC Comics 1986 年至 1987 年出版的《Watchmen》漫畫。時隔近十年，HBO 於去年宣佈將著手製作全新原創影集，並將交由《Lost》編劇 Damon Lindelof 著手，試圖在擁抱原創同名漫畫的懷舊之情的同時，試圖製作出突破性的全新作品。<br />\n<br />\n首波預告中，劇情中的背景似乎延續著 Rorschach 的死後社會，並能看見有個新的神秘組織疑似繼承了 Rorschach 的精神，並頻繁地帶出 DC 世界中的大事件「末日警鐘」氛圍，而警察部分則紛紛套用大量黃色藉以象徵 Watchman 的核心，亦或代表更多的含義。而老年版的 Ozymandias 也於預告中亮相，未來還會有哪些英雄成員加入，想必會是廣大 DC 迷所關注的。<br />\n<br />\n《守護者 Watchmen》預計於今年秋季上線"},{"pid":"4fe785668e9b6b98cc2b0d16126a720f588033c1","tid":1149214,"uid":389,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:18:24.000Z","msg":"留明睇中伏"},{"pid":"8e569a224c2e5968f8073cf8875d36b01b980af2","tid":1149214,"uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:32:30.000Z","msg":"好正咁，仲有邊到有得睇"},{"pid":"1d72e3ce60b2b7e200ef4396f4d91ca21e6e1592","tid":1149214,"uid":21061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:18:09.000Z","msg":"即係冇第二代Rorschach<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b8da7aed2ae0c2ce6ef6cd1819fe012a20a530","tid":1149214,"uid":3358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:33:03.000Z","msg":"同Doomsday clock有連動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbeaffc9c34024b219bbc